next_seeds.title: Enhance CLI Help Section
next_seeds.rationale: Previous audit scores indicate a need for improvement in user interface, particularly command-line related aspects. An enhanced help section can provide better user experience.

next_seeds.title: Implement Robust Error Handling Framework
next_seeds.rationale: Security has never been explored and robust error handling is crucial not only from a security standpoint but also for overall stability of the project. This can serve as an opportunity to enhance both.

next_seeds.title: Optimize Database Query Operations
next_seeds.rationale: While the last audit did focus on performance, there is always room for improving database interactions which are a common bottleneck. Optimizing queries and indexing strategies can offer genuine performance gains.
